Package: StatsTFLValR
Type: Package
Title: Audit-Ready Clinical Validation Utilities for SDTM, ADaM, and TFL Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mangesh", "Kalsekar", 
           email = "kalsem@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: StatsTFLValR provides reusable, audit-ready utilities for 
    statistical programming workflows across SDTM, ADaM, and TFL layers.
    The package includes standardized functions for dataset loading, SUPP 
    merging, derivations, analysis flag checks, Big N and percentage 
    calculations, population counts, TFL table-ready summaries, and 
    PROC COMPARE-style dataset comparison reports. Designed to support
    validation and quality control in clinical trial programming within
    a compliant environment.
